@startuml audio_focus_tmu_notif_to_vcs_voice_state_signal_flow
!theme plain
skinparam backgroundColor #FFFFFF
skinparam defaultFontName Arial
skinparam defaultFontSize 11
skinparam sequenceMessageAlign center
skinparam responseMessageBelowArrow true

title Audio Focus TMU Notif To VCS Voice State Signal Flow\n(audio focus + TMU service + cluster notification -> VCS voice and TTS state)

participant "Audio focus bus" as Audio #F4F7FB
participant "TMU service bus" as TMU #E8F0FE
participant "Cluster notif bus" as Notif #FCE8FF
participant "VCS\nvoice-assist owner" as VCS #E8F7E8
participant "Voice/TTS bus" as VoiceBus #FFF4CC
participant "Observers /\naudio consumers" as Obs #FFF4CC

== VCS Inputs ==

Audio -> VCS : frmAudioFocusMsg\nAudioFocusOwner / AudioDuckingLvl
TMU -> VCS : frmTmuServiceStateMsg\nTmuServiceMode / SignalBars
Notif -> VCS : frmClusterNotifMsg\nClusterNotifType / ClusterNotifArg
activate VCS
VCS -> VCS : clear stale inputs using 300 ms lease windows
VCS -> VCS : voiceAssistState =\nTMU service ? 1 : audio focus ? 2 : 0
VCS -> VCS : wakeWordState =\nTMU service mode 1 and signal bars >= 2
VCS -> VCS : ttsState =\ncluster notif active and audio focus owner > 0
VCS -> VCS : ttsPriority = clusterNotifArg,\nraised to 4 when ducking >= 4
note right of VCS
Representative gating inputs
- AudioFocusOwner
- AudioDuckingLvl
- TmuServiceMode
- SignalBars
- ClusterNotifType / Arg
end note

== VCS Publish ==

VCS -> VoiceBus : frmVoiceAssistStateMsg\nVoiceAssistState / WakeWordState
VCS -> VoiceBus : frmSpeechTtsStateMsg\nTtsState / TtsPriority / TtsQueueDepth
note right of VCS
Representative outputs
- VoiceAssistState
- WakeWordState
- TtsState
- TtsPriority
- TtsQueueDepth
end note

== Downstream Visibility ==

VoiceBus -> Obs : voice/TTS visibility /\nAMP and audio observers
deactivate VCS

note over Audio, Obs
Representative runtime chain
1. Audio focus, TMU service, and cluster notification reach VCS
2. VCS resolves voice-assist posture and wake-word availability
3. VCS derives TTS activation and priority
4. VCS publishes voice and TTS state for downstream audio consumers
end note

@enduml
